The defendant Danielle Rae East was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Danielle Rae East is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Danielle Rae East was found guilty of Possession of Controlled Substance, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(b).
